  "subject": "Use eclipse-temurin:8-jre-alpine docker base image in aai-graphadmin",
  "commit_message": "Use eclipse-temurin:8-jre-alpine docker base image in aai-graphadmin\n\n- use /bin/sh instead of /bin/bash for scripts\n- use wget instead of curl\n- do not check the container user when executing scripts\n\nIssue-ID: AAI-3916\nChange-Id: I3e7c6e47f8eb55f1e2f872e7e427b61fae8232bb\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
